flowRoot.flowPara: At this point, Thuy introduces a more traditional kind of improvisation whereas Henrik and Stefan build a texture that is more of a background. Still the listening is attentive. However, in the greater form, this section did not go so well with the preceding material. So in terms of structural listening, one could say that we failed.
After the first soft section, Thuy introduces a more dynamic material: the continuation of the material already introduced.
Henrik and Stefan immediately pick up Thuy's new initiative, creating a different texture that highlights the new direction in the material.
Stefan and Henrik respond to Thuy's playing with a counterpointing material. (Thuy in turn responds with attentive listening and merges with the new texture).
After the first sequence, Thuy's playing changes, by way of attentive listening to the new structure that Henrik and Stefan introduced.

Thuy brings the new version of the material to a well modulated closure of phrase in the mode of integrated listening (weaving together the texture of Stefan's and Henrik's playing with her own material).
Thuy and Stefan try in different ways to create a crescendo with the current material but this fails, several times. Neither initiative is picked up in the right moment.
